5:
Hee hee... Another day, another good
deed!
7:
Nothing better than saving people in the
name of justice! And I even got some
booty, to boot!
15: Hee hee! You'll never believe this!
19:
I've finally got my hands on a real
legendary treasure map!
24: Wow... And where'd you find this map?
28:
Just now! It must've been fate that
brought me and that old hooded lady
together.
31:
She needed money to take care of her
sick granddaughter, you see.
33:
Being a family heirloom and all, she
didn't wanna sell it, but dire straights,
you know?
36: So you bought it from her?
39:
At first, I just wanted to give her the
money since I didn't need the map.
41:
But she didn't want to accept charity,
so I wound up taking it anyway.
47: That was very kind of you.
57:
H-hold on a second. She didn't strike
you as suspicious at all?
59:
If I didn't know any better, I'd say you
just got swindled...
64: Even if I did, I'm fine with that.
66:
That just means her granddaughter
isn't actually sick at all! Everybody wins
here!
73:
*sigh* I thought you'd say something
like that, but you really ought to be
more vigilant.
76:
I suppose there's no changing you,
though.
80:
Do you plan to search for this treasure,
Lassie?
84:
Treasure hunting? Might be fun.
I AM a sailor, after all!
87: But I've got an even better idea!
96:
I could totally use this map as bait to 
reel in some pirates, and then wipe 'em 
all out in a single go!
101:
A single go?! Wh-what happened to 
meting out proper justice?
106:
This IS justice! Career evildoers 
won't get any mercy from me!
109:
Especially those who threaten 
to taint my beloved seas!
112:
This is what nautical justice is 
all about, baby!
116:
I see. How do you plan on "wiping out" 
these pirates once they've taken your 
bait?
120:
I, uh, I'm sure I'll have something 
cooked up once I get to that point! 
Yeah!
124: Perhaps we could be of assistance?
129:
Could you really? I mean, it'll be 
dangerous... 
Are you sure about that?
134:
Seeing as your plan's about as 
unrealistic as it is naive... yes.
137:
But if you're committing to it, Lassie, 
so are we.
139:
Whatever you plan on doing, 
we've got your back.
143: Wow... Thanks a bunch, you guys!
145:
I might've been separated from my 
crew, but at least I've got you guys 
now!
149:
Hee hee! Now I'm REALLY pumped, 
you guys! Those pirates won't know 
what hit 'em!
